{"tid":1270371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】旗照升，不過無嘉賓","createTime":"2019-06-30T22:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T03:20:31.000Z","uid":140021,"like":676,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"554ebc9a2d644d08638bf83d61d554af693b07f0","tid":1270371,"uid":140021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T22:55:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">七一升旗儀式以雨天方案進行　嘉賓電視視屏看升旗<br />\n<br />\n因天雨關係，在金紫荊廣場舉行的升旗儀式改以雨天方案進行，嘉賓會在會展三樓大會堂通過電視屏幕觀看升旗儀式，慶祝酒會則如期舉行。<br />\nSource: RTHK</span><br />\n<br />\n意思好簡單，你幾大聲點叫都無用，不過支旗就仲喺室外，要點做就交俾你地諗。"},{"pid":"bf47bd855d6f86948a140487bf63a31dbf06cd0f","tid":1270371,"uid":140021,"like":15,"dislike":8,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T22:56:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e800e88481577d00401b60eae6abadeae125fc7","tid":1270371,"uid":72197,"like":4,"dislike":19,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T22:56:46.000Z","msg":"Source？"},{"pid":"a08ab371fe567624e47efe03d081c5276dd8df7d","tid":1270371,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T22:57:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"619bc2a2b474e4a02d0c8a602efbacfe25d8e770","tid":1270371,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e800e88481577d00401b60eae6abadeae125fc7","tid":1270371,"uid":72197,"like":4,"dislike":19,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T22:56:46.000Z","msg":"Source？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T22:57:06.000Z","msg":"Source: RTHK <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9efa86c10b7c126be4aa8b472101abf403a0d12b","tid":1270371,"uid":52621,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e800e88481577d00401b60eae6abadeae125fc7","tid":1270371,"uid":72197,"like":4,"dislike":19,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T22:56:46.000Z","msg":"Source？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T22:57:14.000Z","msg":"香港電台"},{"pid":"f6fc096b4cc4273d9b762daabc7f637769a81a0f","tid":1270371,"uid":140021,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score"